{"tid":1236202,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"文翠珊將向中國副總理提出香港反修例示威問題","createTime":"2019-06-17T11:18:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T12:37:38.000Z","uid":41404,"like":50,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e61127cdd9759e45ac265f580e9c7c374434faa8","tid":1236202,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:18:00.000Z","msg":"英揆發言人：文翠珊將向胡春華提出香港反修例示威問題<br />\n2019-06-17 HKT 19:13<br />\n<br />\n英國首相文翠珊的發言人表示，文翠珊將向中國副總理胡春華提出香港反修訂逃犯條例示威的問題。<br />\n<br />\n胡春華抵達倫敦，出席第十次中英經濟財金對話。<br />\n<br />\n首相發言人表示，香港的大規模遊行，清晰表達反對修訂，英國政府歡迎特區政府注意到市民的關注。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1463451-20190617.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1463451-20190617.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=yUf3ZniyPWjB5eI%2FQURZCgmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=35cf9032\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1463451-20190617.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=0fa4c803\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1463451-20190617.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"29cab67cefdc82c69b113086fd2d3f1e0bc72fc3","tid":1236202,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:20:15.000Z","msg":"估唔到就落台都講嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c075e702e499b1f2f45f07b74c1ccbda8cc56438","tid":1236202,"uid":66669,"like":8,"dislike":9,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:23:31.000Z","msg":"呢個臭婆娘算吧啦<br />\n怕唔之係拎黎同支那R多啲錢就算鳩數"},{"pid":"68c9636e6b2f3a7c2a1bd977d686baec35f5f03d","tid":1236202,"uid":51701,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:26:20.000Z","msg":"may姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知你冇實權嫁啦<br />\n<br />\n做下樣落到佢面就算啦<br />\n<br />\n你老人家頂住班煩膠已經好辛苦嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dd9c8